snippet.title: A Comparative study of the Marilyn MANSON Allegations & Amber HEARD's Allegations- Painting An Essay
snippet.description:
I decided to make this comparative analysis between the two cases due to the rising doubt in the allegations that were recently brought against Manson, as a result from the growing evidence against Amber Heard and her claims of abuse against former husband, Johnny Depp. 

I highly suggest doing your own research, and here are some links to get started if you haven't gone down the rabbit hole yet:

For more information on the Depp- Heard situation:
@Incredibly Average: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ/videos
@SEC: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsEaTDlh3kfgl17DnaRFW2g
@Lost Beyond Pluto: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOp24og-YLLuvUP4yrJ2cJA
All legal documents that are publicly available can be found on the fairfaxcounty website.

For more information on the MM allegations:
@EllieJayden: https://www.youtube.com/user/EllieJayden
MM interview with AV Club: https://music.avclub.com/marilyn-manson-on-charlie-hebdo-the-onion-and-his-gol-1798275764
MM interview with Spin: https://www.spin.com/2009/06/qa-marilyn-manson/
Esmé Bianco's Interview about MM: https://www.thecut.com/2021/02/game-of-thrones-actor-esme-bianco-marilyn-manson.html




#amberheard #marilynmanson #evanrachelwood #justiceforjohnnydepp #watercolor #painting #paintingtimelapse
